  "title": "FOH Team @ BUJA Company",
  "description": "<p><strong>Positions Available</strong></p>\n<p>· Assistant General Manager</p>\n<p>· Server</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Salary and Benefits</strong></p>\n<p>· Employment Type: Full-time (9-hour shifts)</p>\n<p>· Monthly Salary: SGD 2800 - $5000 (Salary depends on experience and position held)</p>\n<p>· Overtime pay (depends on which restaurant you work at)</p>\n<p>· Yearly performance-based bonus / AWS</p>\n<p>· Fixed transportation allowance (depends on which restaurant you work at)</p>\n<p>· Medical coverage, including GP visits and hospitalization</p>\n<p>· Opportunity to work in a state-of-the-art environment</p>\n<p>· Direct mentorship from a Michelin 3-star chef and his team</p>\n<p>· Creative and collaborative work culture</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p>\n<p>· In-depth knowledge of traditional and modern Korean cuisine (preferred)</p>\n<p>· Hospitality degree or relevant certification (preferred)</p>\n<p>· Extensive customer service experiences (preferred)</p>\n<p>· Strong leadership and organizational skills</p>\n<p>· Collaborative spirit with a positive team mindset</p>\n<p>· Familiarity with food safety and sanitation regulations</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>· Collaborate with head chef and kitchen team to ensure seamless communication and coordination</p>\n<p>· Maintain a detailed knowledge of the menu, including seasonal changes and special offerings</p>\n<p>· Maintain excellent and consistent level of customer service, addressing guest concerns promptly and professionally</p>\n<p>· Follow closely on instructions and guidelines set out by Managers</p>\n<p>· Monitor and maintain compliance with safety, hygiene and sanitation regulations</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Location</strong></p>\n<p>· ONMI - 107 Amoy St, Singapore 069927</p>\n<p>· NaOh - 2 Bulim Ave HMGICS, Level 3, 649674</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
